  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Adventures of Pinocchio is a video game, released for the Nintendo DS and Wii on May 8, 2009, developed and published by the now-defunct company Phoenix Games. While there is a variety of mini-games targeted for young children, the game has the peculiarity of having more of a movie, rather than playable portions. A PlayStation 2 version simply called \"Pinocchio,\" was released three years prior the DS and Wii ports' release.",
